Modelos

nnet_model_auto <- 
  nnetar_reg() %>%
    set_engine("nnetar") %>%
    fit(media ~ mes, data = training(splits))
nnet_model_adj <- 
  nnetar_reg(
    seasonal_period = 12,
    non_seasonal_ar = 1,
    seasonal_ar = 1,
    hidden_units = 10,
    num_networks = 20,
    epochs = 500,
    penalty = 0
    ) %>%
    set_engine("nnetar") %>%
    fit(media ~ mes, data = training(splits))
nnet_model_nreg <- 
  nnetar_reg() %>%
    set_engine("nnetar") %>%
    fit(media ~ mes + factor(month(mes, label = TRUE),ordered = FALSE), 
                            data = training(splits))
nnet_model_mreg <- 
  nnetar_reg(
    seasonal_period = 12,
    non_seasonal_ar = 1,
    seasonal_ar = 1,
    hidden_units = 10,
    num_networks = 20,
    epochs = 500,
    penalty = 0) %>%
    set_engine("nnetar") %>%
    fit(media ~ mes+ factor(month(mes, label = TRUE),ordered = FALSE), 
                            data = training(splits))

Comparando os modelos

model_table <- 
modeltime_table(
  nnet_model_auto,
  nnet_model_adj,
  nnet_model_mreg,
  nnet_model_nreg
  
  )

Calibrando

calib_table <- 
  model_table %>% 
  modeltime_calibrate(testing(splits))

Forecast future

future_forecast_tbl <- 
  calib_table %>% 
  modeltime_refit(gold_mean) %>% 
  modeltime_forecast(
    h  = "1 year",
    actual_data = gold_mean
  )
future_forecast_tbl %>% 
  plot_modeltime_forecast()
